## 7. Icons

### Decision: Expo Vector Icons (Lucide icon set)

**Required packages:**
```json
{
  "@expo/vector-icons": "^14.0.0"
}
```

**Rationale:**
- Ships with Expo SDK (zero additional config)
- Lucide = modern, consistent, minimalist design
- Tree-shakeable (only bundle icons actually used)
- Works identically on iOS/Android/Web
- TypeScript autocomplete for icon names
- Scalable vector format (crisp at all sizes)

**Pattern:**
```tsx
import { Lucide } from '@expo/vector-icons'

<Lucide name="calendar" size={24} color="black" />
```

**Forbidden alternatives:**
- ❌ React Native Vector Icons (Expo Vector Icons wraps this, use the wrapper)
- ❌ Custom SVG icon components (unless brand-specific)
- ❌ Image-based icons (not scalable)

